# M4.2 多账号登录与 Token 鉴权

## 里程碑

**M4 扩展** — Web 输入账号名登录；`accounts` 表 + 业务表 `account_id` 隔离；全接口 Bearer 鉴权（除 `/health`、`POST /auth/login`）。

## 关联 Skill

| Skill | 用途 |
|-------|------|
| [entity-service](../Skills/entity-service/SKILL.md) | Account ORM + service |
| [add-api-endpoint](../Skills/add-api-endpoint/SKILL.md) | `POST /auth/login`、router 鉴权 |
| [db-migrate](../Skills/db-migrate/SKILL.md) | `002_accounts_multi_tenant` |
| [http-integration-test](../Skills/http-integration-test/SKILL.md) | auth_test + conftest |

## 范围

### 交付文件

| 文件 | 说明 |
|------|------|
| `server/model/account.py` | Account ORM |
| `server/alembic/versions/002_accounts_multi_tenant.py` | 迁移 + legacy 回填 |
| `server/service/account.py` | login_or_register / get_by_token |
| `server/api/auth.py` | POST /auth/login |
| `utils/bearer_token.py` | parse_bearer_token 纯函数 |
| `server/deps/auth.py` | get_current_account |
| `common/account_context.py` | ContextVar + account_scope |
| `server/routers.py` | 业务 router 统一鉴权 |
| `server/service/{category,budget,transaction}.py` | account_id 过滤 |
| `server/api/agent.py` | account_scope 包裹 invoke |
| `web/src/api/auth.ts` | postLogin + localStorage |
| `web/src/api/client.ts` | authFetch |
| `web/src/components/LoginPage.tsx` | 登录页 |
| `web/src/App.tsx` | 无 token 显示登录 |
| `server/api/auth_test.py` | 登录与 401 用例 |
| `server/api/conftest.py` | auth_token + require_llm |

### 不在范围内

- 密码、OAuth、Token 过期
- Postgres LangGraph checkpointer（M9）
- 修改 architecture.md

## 步骤清单

- [x] 1. Account ORM + 002 迁移；categories/budgets/transactions 加 account_id
- [x] 2. account service、POST /auth/login、bearer_token + get_current_account
- [x] 3. routers 统一鉴权；service 按 account_id 过滤
- [x] 4. account_context + agent_chat scope
- [x] 5. Web LoginPage、authFetch、ChatPage 退出
- [x] 6. conftest + auth_test；各 API 测试适配

## 运行命令

```bash
docker compose up -d
python server/main.py

curl -X POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/auth/login -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{"name":"test"}'
curl -H "Authorization: Bearer <token>" http://127.0.0.1:8000/categories

pytest server/api -v
cd web && npm run serve
```

## 验收标准

- [x] A/B 两账号各自记账，互不可见
- [x] 无 token 访问 `/transactions` → 401
- [x] Agent「我今天花了多少」只统计当前账号（account_scope + resolve_account_id）
- [x] Web 登录后聊天，换账号数据隔离
- [x] `pytest server/api -v` 通过（Agent 测试需 DEEPSEEK_API_KEY）
